{"article_id":"9bN8ckd9ATDqUm3P","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump lamented Senate rules on Twitter on Tuesday","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Congressional negotiators worked with Democrats","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to avert a shutdown until at least September","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"( CNN )","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"President Donald Trump tweeted Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that the country needs a `` good 'shutdown , ' ''","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"as well advocated for changing Senate rules , in a pair of tweets","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"where he complained about the congressional negotiating process .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"`` The reason for the plan","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"negotiated between the Republicans and Democrats","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"is that we need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"which are not there !","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"We ... either elect more Republican Senators in 2018","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"or change the rules now to 51 % .","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Our country needs a good 'shutdown ' in September","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to fix mess ! ''","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Trump said Tuesday in two consecutive tweets .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"The reason for the plan","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"negotiated between the Republicans and Democrats","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"is that we need 60 votes in the Senate","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"which are not there !","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"We ....","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"either elect more Republican Senators in 2018","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"or change the rules now to 51 % .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Our country needs a good `` shutdown '' in September","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"to fix mess !","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Democrats quickly hopped on Trump 's call for a shutdown ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"including Hawaii Sen. Brian Schatz ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"who tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"`` The President just called for a government shutdown this fall .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"No President has ever done anything like this . '' The President just called for a government shutdown this fall .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"No President has ever done anything like this .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"- Brian Schatz","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"( @ brianschatz )","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"May 2 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Congressional leaders announced Sunday","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that they 'd reached a deal","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"to avert a government shutdown until September .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The deal did not include several Trump campaign promises","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"-- including money for a border wall --","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"in part because GOP leaders needed Democratic votes","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"to pass the deal in the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Office of Management and Budget director Mick Mulvaney on Tuesday took to the White House briefing room","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"to slam Democrats ' claims of victory in the budget deal ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"arguing","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"that Trump secured a large increase in defense spending","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"and pushed border wall funding to its highest level in a decade .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":107,"left":0,"right":106,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":57,"right":105,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":57,"left":56,"right":4,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":56,"left":1,"r